This will allow you to create a fun and functional way to use Voice Monkey as a TTS to your echo devices.

You need the following:
1. an amazon account
2. at least 1 echo device
3. the alexa media player integration in Home Assistant
4. Voicemonkey.io account
5. link the Voicemonkey skill in your alexa account

The code in this repository will allow you to create a card on your dashboard that can be used to trigger text to speech to come out of your echo device.
